  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Kajiya.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Kajiya Clan, Level 4+</p><p>Your knowledge of equipment seals has allowed you to learn how to remove and replace them on the fly.</p><ul><li><p>Increase your Charisma by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>As an action on your turn, you may move any equipment seals from armor or weapons straight to armor sets or weapons that have empty Seal Slots.</p></li><li><p>When in possession of an item that has Equipment Seals attached, you may remove those seals as an action and place them in your inventory. These Seals are viable for up to 1 week and must be attached to an armor set or weapon before they lose viability.</p></li></ul>",
